Changelog
---------

v0.5.2 2017-12-06
=================

 - max_frame_length as input parameter
 - first unit tests
 - minor cleanups

v0.5.1 2017-11-19
=================

 - Changed libwebsocket to static linking to avoid problems with 2 instances of the library running

v0.5.0 2017-11-18
=================

 - First release with initial support to connect, subscribe and receive messages
   though websockets
 - Important known bugs and limitations:
   - only 1 instance can be running at a time
   - fixed STOMP_MAX_FRAME_BUFFER to 2048   
  